              <h2>Installation guide</h2>
              
              <p>
                <b><span class="caps">WARNING</span></b>: Locomotive is in beta but already used in production with success. Want a proof ? This website is served by Locomotive !
              </p>
              
              <p>
                You suggest you to start to read the <a href="/support/installation/requirements">requirements</a> section. Then choose one of the installation methods.<br/> If you want to test Locomotive and sneak into the code, we recommend you the <a href="/support/installation/source">from source</a> installation.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                Let us know if you have any <a href="http://locomotive.vanillaforums.com/categories/requested-features">suggestions</a> or if you find <a href="http://locomotive.vanillaforums.com/categories/problems">bugs</a>.
              </p>
              
